OL,3,CWintry conditions will be felt on
OL,4,CFriday as wind, snow and ice warnings
OL,5,Cin place
OL,7,FYou might have already battled with an
OL,8,Fumbrella on Thursday as heavy rain and
OL,9,Fstrong winds battered parts of the UK.
OL,10,FIt is set to continue.
OL,12,FTemperatures are about to drop as a
OL,13,Fcolder spell is expected to bring the
OL,14,Frisk of snow and frost overnight and
OL,15,Finto Friday, particularly across
OL,16,Fnorthern areas.
OL,18,FThe Met Office has issued yellow wind
OL,19,Fwarnings for several regions, with
OL,20,Fgusts of 50 to 70mph possible in
OL,21,Fexposed and coastal locations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
