PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773349953
OL,3,CWintry conditions will be felt on
OL,4,CFriday as wind, snow and ice warnings
OL,5,Cin place
OL,7,FThese conditions could lead to some
OL,8,Ftravel disruption, especially for high-
OL,9,Fsided vehicles, ferries and rail
OL,10,Fservices.
OL,12,FWhat is causing the windy weather?
OL,14,FThe winds are being driven by an area
OL,15,Fof low pressure to the south of
OL,16,FIceland, bringing a blustery and
OL,17,Funsettled day for many.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773349953
OL,3,CWintry conditions will be felt on
OL,4,CFriday as wind, snow and ice warnings
OL,5,Cin place
OL,7,FAs this system clears later, colder
OL,8,Fair will move in from the north,
OL,9,Fallowing conditions to turn
OL,10,Fincreasingly wintry overnight.
OL,12,FWill it snow?
OL,14,FSnow showers are possible from late
OL,15,FThursday evening and into Friday
OL,16,Fmorning.
OL,18,FThis will likely only cause a light
OL,19,Fcovering of snow for areas on higher
OL,20,Fground and in parts of Scotland and
OL,21,Fnorthern England.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
