FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773349953
OL,3,CWintry conditions will be felt on
OL,4,CFriday as wind, snow and ice warnings
OL,5,Cin place
OL,7,FAt lower levels, precipitation may
OL,8,Ffall as a mix of rain and sleet at
OL,9,Ffirst, although snow could briefly
OL,10,Fsettle in a few spots during the early
OL,11,Fhours as temperatures fall.
OL,13,FA yellow snow and ice warning has been
OL,14,Fissued for parts of Scotland, coming
OL,15,Finto force at midnight on Friday
OL,16,Fmorning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
