PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773349953
OL,3,CWintry conditions will be felt on
OL,4,CFriday as wind, snow and ice warnings
OL,5,Cin place
OL,7,FJason Kelly, Chief Operational
OL,8,FMeteorologist for the Met Office said:
OL,9,F"A notable shift in wind direction to
OL,10,Fa north-westerly flow will bring a
OL,11,Fmarkedly colder day nationwide on
OL,12,FFriday, with the potential for a
OL,13,Fmixture of sunny spells, heavy
OL,14,Fshowers, coastal gales, and snow over
OL,15,Fhigh ground."
OL,17,FHow cold will it get?
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
