OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773349953
OL,3,CWintry conditions will be felt on
OL,4,CFriday as wind, snow and ice warnings
OL,5,Cin place
OL,7,FOvernight lows are expected to drop
OL,8,Fclose to or below freezing in rural
OL,9,Fareas, allowing frost and icy patches
OL,10,Fto form on untreated roads and
OL,11,Fpavements.
OL,13,FTemperatures could be around 3-5C and
OL,14,Ffeel close to freezing, 10C below
OL,15,FThursday's temperatures.
OL,17,FThis could make for a tricky start to
OL,18,Fthe day for some commuters on Friday
OL,19,Fmorning.
OL,21,FWill it last through the weekend?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773349953
OL,3,CWintry conditions will be felt on
OL,4,CFriday as wind, snow and ice warnings
OL,5,Cin place
OL,7,FThe colder conditions are likely to
OL,8,Fcontinue into the start of the
OL,9,Fweekend, with a frosty start possible
OL,10,Fon Saturday.
OL,12,FHowever, the cold spell looks set to
OL,13,Fbe fairly brief, as milder and more
OL,14,Funsettled weather returns from the
OL,15,Fwest on Sunday.
OL,17,FSo if you're out and about on Friday,
OL,18,Fwrap up warm as it might feel rather
OL,19,Fchilly compared to the spring sunshine
OL,20,Fwarmth we had last week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
